{"tid":1082725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"風大頂唔順！KAWS公仔提早離港 粉絲不捨追住合照","createTime":"2019-03-29T06:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T06:56:21.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"35801f64d7bbdf2902989194bda3161c29627c5b","tid":1082725,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VE3rseW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVE3rseW.png&h=c6d8113c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZVJuth.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZVJuth.png&h=1a634cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckMD2Oi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckMD2Oi.png&h=5b718af9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3MTRGE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3MTRGE.png&h=d5120b04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rD3yRGE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrD3yRGE.png&h=dea14ca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本計劃在維港「瞓」至本周日（31日）的 KAWS招牌公仔COMPANION，因主辦單位擔心周末期間風勢轉趨凌厲，決定提早至今日離場。全長37米的COMPANION今早已在維港海面自我「放氣」，中午前已變回一塊平面塑膠在海上漂浮，等候工作人員到場收回。<br />\n<br />\n連日在中西區海濱長廊對開海面漂浮的COMPANION已成為該區一個「打卡」熱點，如今它要提早離場，不少市民都站在岸邊目送它打回原形。有粉絲不想錯過合照機會，即使COMPANION已經漏氣，仍拿起手機把握機會和它合照。主辦單位則派出大型躉船接載工作人員到場協助收回COMPANION。<br />\n<br />\n雙眼「打交叉」的COMPANION公仔是美國藝術家KAWS的標誌性設計，今次原定是以香港作為《KAWS:HOLIDAY》第三站展出，希望透過平躺在維港漂浮的COMPANION，喚醒終日低頭營營役役的港人是時候放鬆一下，抬頭望望天空放下生活重擔。"}]}